fullplot: Followup movie to the TV series about 250,000 aliens, or "newcomers" as they are known, who have by now settled alongside the humans in California. Most of the newcomers were slaves, and the slave masters are now looking for them. They send Aponso to earth to locate the slaves ready for the aliens to pick them up.
plot: Alien life form comes to Earth to rescue his enslaved race.
title: Alien Nation: Dark Horizon
